{"tid":765841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有事主圖] 男女青年清晨於海濱公園打野戰 稱酒後失控今判守行為","createTime":"2018-08-03T05:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T08:46:31.000Z","uid":6446,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"97153c9465bcd1ec9fdead6505cc9628e803f727","tid":765841,"uid":6446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T05:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180803/large/1533271445_94d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180803%2Flarge%2F1533271445_94d0.jpg&h=97b14e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n途人於今年5月13日清晨五時，於觀塘海濱公園某燈柱附近，發現一對男女形跡可疑，於是報警。警方到場發現兩人下身赤裸、男上女下的正在交歡，於是喝停兩人。兩人警誡下承認因酒後失控而犯案。<br />\n<br />\n男女被告陳尤斌（23歲）及陳嘉欣(20歲)原被控作出有違公德行為罪，控方今撤控改以簽保守行為處理。在兩人同意下，兩人須以1,000元簽保守行為一年，並各須付500元訟費。<br />\n兩人離開法庭時，男方大方讓記者拍照，見女方被追訪，即挺身護花走在女方前頭。<br />\n【案件編號:KTCC1663/18】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180803/58518654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180803%2F58518654&d=3qbCDYsWA4zLZmsCRWad2P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=137bfb77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180803%2F58518654&h=856c5abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180803/58518654</a>"},{"pid":"3a4a64756f46517624d3bdd1412f46ccdf22e7d9","tid":765841,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:00:43.000Z","msg":"陳嘉欣以為無線果個"},{"pid":"c5ea8fe1fdc689e913c3ad34de18927b38c974fd","tid":765841,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9fb238cf2b9c044e2e1f33b79622eaaa9329f5","tid":765841,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":38,"score":-36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018